(511, 'Heads up note 2026-01-23T16:35:00.000+05:30: Hi team, Sharing the heads-up note for our investment in [VoiceBit](https://www.voicebit.ai/) This is an AI voice agent for restaurant phone ordering automation that handles end-to-end operations including payments, loyalty, web ordering, and delivery - building towards becoming the new age system of record for direct ordering ("Zoca for Restaurants") DeVC is investing $200K as part of a ~$2M round @ $10M post money valuation led by 1984 VC We were introduced to the founders by [Samit Kalra](https://www.linkedin.com/in/samit-kalra-a6179365) (Partner at 1984 VC) This is a Core Cheque & our 2nd investment with 1984 VC (our first deal with them was Orange Slice - YC S25) **Founders** 1. [**Hitesh Kenjale**](https://www.linkedin.com/in/hiteshkenjale)** - CEO** 1. Berkeley MBA 1. 2x venture-backed founder (DesiHangover - grassroot footwear maker in India) 1. Reference check with [Abha Agrawal](https://www.linkedin.com/in/abha-agrawal-72439654) (ex-CoFo @ Desi Hangover): 1. *++ Used to be entrepreneurial always. Trying lot of side hustles. * 1. *++ Stand out superpower: dependable holistically to solve problems. * 1. *++ Passionate about numbers and moves fast. ++ Process oriented and focused. * 1. *?? Weakness: Should disconnect himself from people problem solving that aren''t critical. Tries to solve for too much for everyone. * 1. *?? When span of work expands, prioritization he needs to mature more than where he is. * 1. *Would you ba...'),
